name: StudiwerkTrier(EN)
0:
”Alexa, open Studiwerk Trier”
”Alexa, ask Studiwerk Trier, what is for dinner today”
”Alexa, ask Studiwerk Trier, what is the DiMiDo program for today”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: studiwerk trier
des: With the new Skill of the Studierendenwerk Trier, you can conveniently call up the current menu or the current DiMiDo programme. Simply ask "Alexa, ask Studiwerk Trier, what's on the menu today" or "Alexa, ask Studiwerk Trier for the DiMiDo program of today".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
